```plantuml
@startuml McOrts_taller-iot-sensor_radiactividad
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "ESP8266\n(WEMOS D1 mini Pro)" as ESP8266 #lightyellow {
  rectangle "MQTT\nClient" as MQTTClient #lightblue
  rectangle "Geiger Counter\nModule" as GeigerCounter #lightgreen
}

rectangle "MQTT Broker" as MQTTBroker #mistyrose

rectangle "Node-RED" as NodeRED #aliceblue

rectangle "GMC.MAP" as GMCMap #lightsteelblue

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> ESP8266 : configure Wi-Fi\n& MQTT settings

' ESP8266 interactions
GeigerCounter --> ESP8266 : detect radiation\n(pulses)
ESP8266 --> MQTTClient : calculate CPM\nfrom pulses
MQTTClient --> MQTTBroker : publish CPM data
MQTTBroker --> MQTTClient : send LED control\ncommands

' Node-RED interactions
MQTTBroker --> NodeRED : transmit CPM data
NodeRED --> GMCMap : process & display\non map

' User interactions
User --> NodeRED : view radiation data
@enduml
```